            "[Add your acceptance of terms content here. This section should explain that by using the service, users agree to be bound by these terms.]"
          )}
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-4">
          {gettext("2. Description of Service")}
        </h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-content">
          {gettext(
            "[Describe your service, what it provides, and any limitations or disclaimers about the service.]"
          )}
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-4">
          {gettext("3. User Accounts and Registration")}
        </h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-content">
          {gettext(
            "[Explain account creation requirements, user responsibilities for account security, and account termination policies.]"
          )}
