      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-4">
          {gettext("4. User Conduct and Prohibited Uses")}
        </h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-content">
          {gettext(
            "[List prohibited activities, acceptable use policies, and consequences for violations.]"
          )}
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-4">
          {gettext("5. Intellectual Property Rights")}
        </h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-content">
          {gettext(
            "[Address ownership of content, trademarks, copyrights, and user-generated content rights.]"
          )}
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-4">
          {gettext("6. Payment and Billing")}
        </h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-content">
          {gettext(
            "[If applicable, include pricing, payment terms, refund policies, and billing procedures.]"
          )}
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-4">
          {gettext("7. Privacy Policy")}
        </h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-content">
          {gettext(
            "[Reference your privacy policy and how user data is collected, used, and protected.]"
          )}
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-4">
          {gettext("8. Disclaimers and Limitation of Liability")}
        </h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-content">
          {gettext(
            "[Include liability limitations, service disclaimers, and warranty disclaimers.]"
          )}
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-4">
          {gettext("9. Indemnification")}
        </h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-content">
          {gettext(
            "[Explain user responsibilities for indemnifying the company against claims arising from their use of the service.]"
          )}
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-4">
          {gettext("10. Termination")}
        </h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-content">
          {gettext(
            "[Describe conditions under which the service or user accounts may be terminated.]"
          )}
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-4">
          {gettext("11. Changes to Terms")}
        </h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-content">
          {gettext("[Explain how and when terms may be updated and how users will be notified.]")}
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-4">
          {gettext("12. Governing Law and Jurisdiction")}
        </h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-content">
          {gettext(
            "[Specify which laws govern the agreement and where disputes will be resolved.]"
          )}
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-4">
          {gettext("13. Contact Information")}
        </h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-content">
          {gettext(
            "[Provide contact information for legal inquiries and questions about these terms.]"
          )}
        </p>
